The desire was strong but when it wasn't fulfilled it caused suffering
Had I paid some attention to whether my practice was right or wrong I might have come to my senses enough to have evaluated things to have abandoned some of my bullheaded attachments or to have cut back on my desires so that the suffering would have become lighter
